            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A docile wolliped uses the low attack bonus from the combatant array for its gore attack. The wolliped loses this weakness if trained for combat, a function of the rear a wild animal task of the Survival skill. A wolliped trained this way uses the high attack bonus for its gore attack and adds the knockdown critical hit effect.",
